<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>Privacy Policy - HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM Guide</title>
    <meta name="description"
        content="Understand how the her-trees.com HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM community guide collects, stores, and protects limited personal data." />
    <meta name="robots" content="follow, index, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large" />

    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">

    <link rel="canonical" href="https://her-trees.com/privacypolicy" />
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <%-include('header')%>
        <main id="body">
            <section class="py-3">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-9 mx-auto">
                            <article class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                <h1 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
                                <p><strong>Last updated: March 20, 2026</strong></p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Who We Are</h2>
                                <p>Her-trees.com is a third-party guide that aggregates publicly available information
                                    about
                                    <strong>HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM</strong>, the Stone-developed puzzle adventure
                                    released on
                                    February 11, 2026. We are not owned by Stone and we do not run player accounts; this
                                    site is
                                    purely informational.
                                </p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Contact messages:</strong> If you email us at support@her-trees.com, we
                                        receive the
                                        email address and any optional details you include.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> Our hosting provider automatically records IP
                                        addresses,
                                        browser type, and timestamps to prevent abuse and diagnose performance issues.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">How We Use Data</h2>
                                <p>We process the limited personal data described above to respond to support requests,
                                    maintain
                                    security, and understand which pages are most helpful. We do not sell or rent
                                    personal data
                                    and we do not run behavioral advertising.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Cookies &amp; Third-Party Content</h2>
                                <p>Her-trees.com sets only essential cookies (for load balancing and remembering
                                    dismissals of UI
                                    elements). Embedded game demos hosted on itch.io or other storefronts may set their
                                    own
                                    cookies. Those cookies are controlled by their respective providers, and you should
                                    consult
                                    their privacy notices for details.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Data Retention</h2>
                                <p>Support emails are stored for up to twelve months so we can track resolutions.
                                    Aggregated
                                    analytics data is retained for up to twenty-four months. Server logs rotate
                                    automatically and
                                    are deleted within thirty days unless needed to investigate abuse.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Legal Bases (EEA &amp; UK Visitors)</h2>
                                <p>Where the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) applies, we rely on the following
                                    legal bases:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> for basic analytics and security logging.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong>Consent</strong> when you voluntarily email us.</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
                                <p>Depending on your location, you may request access, correction, deletion, or
                                    restriction of the
                                    personal data we store about you. Send requests to <a
                                        href="mailto:support@her-trees.com">support@her-trees.com</a>
                                    and include enough information for us to locate your data. We will respond within
                                    thirty days.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Children's Privacy</h2>
                                <p>This site is intended for visitors aged 16 or older. If we learn that a child under
                                    16 has
                                    submitted personal data, we will delete it promptly.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Changes to This Policy</h2>
                                <p>We may update this document when we add new features or change analytics tools. When
                                    that
                                    happens we will revise the "Last updated" date above and keep prior versions on file
                                    for
                                    reference.</p>

                                <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Contact</h2>
                                <p>Questions about privacy can be emailed to <a
                                        href="mailto:support@her-trees.com">support@her-trees.com</a>.
                                    If you need a postal address for formal correspondence, email us first so we can
                                    provide the
                                    appropriate mailing details.</p>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%-include('footer')%>
</body>

</html>
